Happy 4th of July 🇺🇸🎇🌭
In honor of America’s birthday… we’re giving away A SUMMER’S SUPPLY OF CRUNCH!!! ☀️🏖️🧺🥨

TO ENTER:
1. Follow us @PRETZELIZED on IG.
2. Like this post.
3. Tag someone to #ShareYourCrunch with. Note: you can enter multiple times by tagging different friends.
4. Share to your story and tag @PRETZELIZED for an extra chance to win!

WHAT YOU'LL WIN:
• 2 variety cases of all your favorite PRETZELIZED Pretzel Pita Chips (summer's supply)!
• A branded PRETZELIZED picnic blanket for all your outdoor adventures.
• A branded PRETZELIZED cooler bag to keep your snacks and drinks perfectly chilled.

*Giveaway ends on 8/01/25 at 11:59 PM EST. Must be within the US to be qualified to win. This giveaway is in no way sponsored, endorsed or administered by, or associated with Meta/Instagram. Must be 18+ to enter. We will DM the winner, we will NOT request any Credit Card information or create a page for you to follow in regards to winning the prize. No purchase necessary.
